### Compare Length - Equal
POST https://localhost:5001/api/quantitymeasurement/compare
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "quantity1": {
    "value": 12,
    "unit": "INCH",
    "measurementType": "LENGTH"
  },
  "quantity2": {
    "value": 1,
    "unit": "FEET",
    "measurementType": "LENGTH"
  }
}

###

### Compare Temperature
POST https://localhost:5001/api/quantitymeasurement/compare
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "quantity1": {
    "value": 0,
    "unit": "CELSIUS",
    "measurementType": "TEMPERATURE"
  },
  "quantity2": {
    "value": 32,
    "unit": "FAHRENHEIT",
    "measurementType": "TEMPERATURE"
  }
}

###

### Convert Feet to Inches
POST https://localhost:5001/api/quantitymeasurement/convert
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "quantity": {
    "value": 1,
    "unit": "FEET",
    "measurementType": "LENGTH"
  },
  "targetUnit": "INCH"
}

###

### Convert Celsius to Fahrenheit
POST https://localhost:5001/api/quantitymeasurement/convert
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "quantity": {
    "value": 100,
    "unit": "CELSIUS",
    "measurementType": "TEMPERATURE"
  },
  "targetUnit": "FAHRENHEIT"
}

###

### Add Lengths
POST https://localhost:5001/api/quantitymeasurement/add
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "quantity1": {
    "value": 2,
    "unit": "INCH",
    "measurementType": "LENGTH"
  },
  "quantity2": {
    "value": 2,
    "unit": "INCH",
    "measurementType": "LENGTH"
  }
}

###

### Add Weights
POST https://localhost:5001/api/quantitymeasurement/add
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "quantity1": {
    "value": 1,
    "unit": "KILOGRAM",
    "measurementType": "WEIGHT"
  },
  "quantity2": {
    "value": 1000,
    "unit": "GRAM",
    "measurementType": "WEIGHT"
  }
}

###

### Subtract Volumes
POST https://localhost:5001/api/quantitymeasurement/subtract
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "quantity1": {
    "value": 1,
    "unit": "LITRE",
    "measurementType": "VOLUME"
  },
  "quantity2": {
    "value": 500,
    "unit": "MILLILITRE",
    "measurementType": "VOLUME"
  }
}

###

### Divide Lengths
POST https://localhost:5001/api/quantitymeasurement/divide
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "quantity1": {
    "value": 10,
    "unit": "FEET",
    "measurementType": "LENGTH"
  },
  "quantity2": {
    "value": 2,
    "unit": "FEET",
    "measurementType": "LENGTH"
  }
}

###

### Temperature Addition (Should Fail)
POST https://localhost:5001/api/quantitymeasurement/add
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "quantity1": {
    "value": 100,
    "unit": "CELSIUS",
    "measurementType": "TEMPERATURE"
  },
  "quantity2": {
    "value": 50,
    "unit": "CELSIUS",
    "measurementType": "TEMPERATURE"
  }
}

###

### Cross-Category Operation (Should Fail)
POST https://localhost:5001/api/quantitymeasurement/add
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "quantity1": {
    "value": 1,
    "unit": "FEET",
    "measurementType": "LENGTH"
  },
  "quantity2": {
    "value": 1,
    "unit": "KILOGRAM",
    "measurementType": "WEIGHT"
  }
}
